analysis/outputs/phase10_docking/hsa_chainA.pdb
analysis/outputs/phase10_docking/hsa_receptor.pdbqt
analysis/outputs/phase10_docking/ligands/
analysis/outputs/phase10_docking/*.log
analysis/outputs/phase10_docking/test_*.pdbqt
analysis/outputs/deck_assets/
# Phase 13 fatty-tail CREST runs: KEEP crest_conformers.xyz (the only file the
# Phase-6 parser needs; energies are in its comment lines), plus small provenance
# (crest_best.xyz, run.log, crest.energies, the <name>.xyz input, sbatch/SUBMIT.md).
# Everything below is bulky/regenerable CREST scratch — never commit it:
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/crest_dynamics.trj
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/confcross.xyz
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/crest_rotamers.xyz
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/gfnff_topo
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/crest.restart
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/crestopt.log
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/*.xtbrestart
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/*.xtbtopo.mol
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/wbo
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/*.[0-9]*.out
analysis/outputs/phase13_qm_runs/**/*.[0-9]*.err

